{"tid":648112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汪精衛用廣東話解釋中日合作理由!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-04-30T11:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T02:25:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"d37006aa10f1a40cacdbe30f87b3f314e20f0aa4","tid":648112,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:44:50.000Z","msg":"1939年 被大部份中國人定性為(大漢奸)《汪精衛1883-1944》生於廣東三水縣（今佛山市三水區），清末秀才、官費留學生，畢業於日本法政大學，〔汪精衛〕用自己母語廣東話講述中日合作理由，最後說主要反共產黨!<br />\n<br />\n片段是1934年至1944年中國，1943年親日派汪精衛國民政府，出席鴉片戰爭一百年演講，發表反英興亞演講（日本大東亞共榮），之後汪精衛對英國宣戰。1944年11月10日病死於日本名古屋大學醫院，後移返中國南京舉行葬禮珍貴片段。汪精衛年青時滿腔愛國，最後成為《漢奸》代名詞。  <br />\n<br />\nwai tse 【歷史時空】整理<br />\n&darr;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2021670614786179/videos/2144351062518133/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2021670614786179%2Fvideos%2F2144351062518133%2F&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c2456256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2021670614786179/videos/2144351062518133/</a>"},{"pid":"95b8a2b6d1c0f8affa64742758f0ae31f54fa5b4","tid":648112,"uid":125516,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:47:28.000Z","msg":"好搞笑以前啲廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b099c763843480c1895e5c7aad6f667751a3ba0","tid":648112,"uid":3465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b8a2b6d1c0f8affa64742758f0ae31f54fa5b4","tid":648112,"uid":125516,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:47:28.000Z","msg":"好搞笑以前啲廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"啲style好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c94740f2bb830c2f73503351be56b6ff0dba3f9","tid":648112,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"